{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"不然，你们却选择今世的生活；"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"其实，后世是更好的，是更长久的。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"这确是载在古经典中的，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"载在易卜拉欣和穆萨的经典中的。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"大灾的消息，确已降临你了，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"在那日，将有许多人是恭敬的、"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"劳动的、辛苦的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他们将入烈火，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"将饮沸泉，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他们没有食物，但有荆棘，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"既不肥人，又不能充饥；"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"在那日，将有许多人，是享福的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"是为其劳绩而愉快的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"他们将在崇高的乐园中，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"听不到恶言，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"里面有流泉，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"里面有高榻，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"有陈设着的杯盏，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"有排列着的靠枕，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"有铺展开的绒毯。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"难道他们不观察吗？骆驼是怎样造成的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"天是怎样被升高的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"山峦是怎样被竖立起的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"大地是怎样被展开的。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"你当教诲，你只是教诲（他们的），"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"你绝不是监察他们的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"但谁转身离去而且不信教，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"安拉将以最大的刑罚惩治谁。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"他们必定只归于我，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"他们的稽核，必定由我负责。"}]}